  "2217740": {
    "name": "Kitty Survivors: Rogues of Catmere",
    "steam_appid": 2217740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/c5e914483f413413c777283abac23c10.poster.avif?t=1763147162\" width=600 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/c5e914483f413413c777283abac23c10.webm?t=1763147162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/c5e914483f413413c777283abac23c10.mp4?t=1763147162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《小猫生存者》中，您扮演一名猫公会成员，受雇保护Catmere王国。在一个充满魔法、爆炸和当然还有... 小猫的土地上，抵御一波波的被诅咒的生物！努力存活足够长的时间，面对您最大的敌人，伟大的Walter Spray博士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设通往胜利的道路</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择多种技能组合，尝试找到适合您的完美组合！您可能想生下一只小猫，在战斗中帮助您，或者您可能想患上爆炸性腹泻，消灭您的敌人。一切由您决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >锻造厂</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个木箱，一个矮人胡须和一个肌肉发达的栗鼠，这些东西有什么共同之处呢？在错误的手中，没有什么共同之处，但您是一位经验丰富的铁匠，可以利用任何您想要的东西锻造出终极武器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/74c72e9d04722b42cdf8d6c049a2ef55.poster.avif?t=1763147162\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/74c72e9d04722b42cdf8d6c049a2ef55.webm?t=1763147162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/74c72e9d04722b42cdf8d6c049a2ef55.mp4?t=1763147162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >宠物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的奔跑中，你可以获得蛋并孵化它们，得到忠诚的伙伴。在战斗中使用它们，喂养它们苹果，看它们进化为最终形态！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/1fec5d35b926399ea0c33f5f4104a09f.poster.avif?t=1763147162\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/1fec5d35b926399ea0c33f5f4104a09f.webm?t=1763147162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217740/extras/1fec5d35b926399ea0c33f5f4104a09f.mp4?t=1763147162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动和手动开火和瞄准选项</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可在15分钟内完成的奔跑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次奔跑都有独特的构建</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有不同技能的角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有升级系统和进化的宠物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器制作，有一千多种组合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六种武器类型：弓、法杖、回旋镖、迷你机枪、霰弹枪和鱼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特而有趣的特权</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精英和首领</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永久升级</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢您阅读到这里！我是一名独立游戏开发者，非常感谢您对我的游戏的兴趣！战胜生物，尝试不同的构建，尽情享受。哦，别忘了与朋友分享！无论如何，再次感谢，希望您有个愉快的一天！</p>",
